ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 233, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 233 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK, with respect to the severe rainstorm that occurred from November 30, 2020 to December 2, 2020.
